# Thank you for your contribution!

### Please fill this template

---

### Description

_**REQUIRED** - Provide a clear and concise description of the change_

```text
Example: Implemented endpoint for updating appointment.
```

---

### Type of change

_**REQUIRED** - What was the main point of this change?_

- [ ] New feature (non-breaking change which adds functionality)
- [ ] Improvement (enhancement to existing functionality)
- [ ] Performance improvement
- [ ] UI / UX enhancement

---

### Dependencies added / modified

_Add the dependencies that was added or modified in this change_

```text
Example: org.wiremock > wiremock > 3.13.2
```

### Testing

#### Checklist

_**REQUIRED** - Check if all tests were created_

- [ ] Unit tests added / modified
- [ ] Integration tests added / modified
- [ ] Pact tests added / modified
- [ ] Manual tests completed

#### Filenames

_**REQUIRED** - Add the filename of all the tests added / modified_

- TestClassOne.java
- TestClassTwo.java
- TestClassThree.java

### Documentation

_Select which documentation was updated_

- [ ] README updated
- [ ] API documentation updated
- [ ] Code comments added
- [ ] CHANGELOG entry added

---

### Checklist

_**REQUIRED** - Make sure your change follows the guidelines_

- [ ] My code follows the project's style guidelines
- [ ] I have performed a self-review of my code
- [ ] I have commented my code, particularly in hard-to-understand areas
- [ ] I have made corresponding changes to the documentation
- [ ] My changes generate no new warnings
- [ ] I have added tests that prove my fix is effective or that my feature works
- [ ] New and existing unit tests pass locally with my changes
- [ ] Any dependent changes have been merged and published
